video.title: Darknet
video.synopsis: A macabre web site called Darknet links the tales in this chilling anthology series whose protagonists face a range of unnameable horrors.

episodes.synopsis: A man follows a trail of strange objects in some lockers to a shocking discovery; a medical student suspects somebody is breaking into her place.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: A young cop questions a beautiful woman about a murder in her building; in a hotel room, a stressed businesswoman puts on a show for a peeping tom.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: A phone installer shows up at an apartment, setting off a shocking chain of events; a salesman hires an escort and gets more than he bargained for.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: A hospitalized woman, unable to move or speak, knows her attacker is back; a suicide hot line operator pleads with a caller to save his own life.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: An office worker discovers an enigmatic postcard; a woman is emailed a series of videos showing people being murdered.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: A laundromat worker witnesses a murder and tries not to be the next victim; two teens' escalating cyberpranks on each other backfire badly.
episodes.title: Episode 6
